WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.780
In modern times, we've gotten used to the images of dystopian societies in fiction,

00:05.140 --> 00:09.080
from a world where babies are no longer being born and children of men,

00:09.580 --> 00:14.840
to the use of human-like artificial intelligence as slaves in a dying world like Blade Runner,

00:14.980 --> 00:20.620
or the very bleak future of The Matrix, where our entire reality is a managed simulation,

00:20.920 --> 00:25.420
keeping us docile, just so that our bodies can be used for energy.

00:25.660 --> 00:28.840
There is an acceptance of the dystopia they survive in.

00:28.840 --> 00:32.860
Like the proverbial frog sat in slowly boiling water.

00:33.200 --> 00:39.240
And one only need to shift their perspective slightly to realize that the world we are currently living in

00:39.240 --> 00:42.920
shares many characteristics of these dystopias.

00:43.340 --> 00:47.680
Or at the very least, there exist some extremely worrying trends.

00:47.920 --> 00:51.160
Trends that might produce a future where food makes you sick,

00:51.380 --> 00:54.000
going to the doctor can bankrupt your entire family,

00:54.600 --> 00:57.880
social interactions have been reduced into likes and upvotes,

00:57.880 --> 01:01.760
and you can barely even tell if the person responding to you is AI.

01:02.440 --> 01:06.540
We live in a society where panels of self-appointed quote-unquote experts

01:06.540 --> 01:10.140
decide what you're allowed to hear, think, and remember.

01:10.700 --> 01:12.760
We're told what's real and what isn't,

01:12.920 --> 01:15.640
and anything that doesn't fit the script is dismissed.

01:16.320 --> 01:19.020
These things are treated not as mysteries to be explored,

01:19.260 --> 01:21.920
but as distractions, a punchline of a joke.

01:21.980 --> 01:23.420
Don't get him too close to me, please.

01:23.420 --> 01:27.300
It seems clear that a system has been put in place to deceive us,

01:27.680 --> 01:30.960
and this does not end at the limits of what you can see in the sky.

01:31.600 --> 01:35.980
This deception reaches down into the fundamental building blocks of your body,

01:36.140 --> 01:38.220
what you eat, why you get sick,

01:38.580 --> 01:41.660
and how that disease and treatment is commodified.

01:41.660 --> 01:45.940
It's not a wildly outlandish claim to suggest that a blanket,

01:46.260 --> 01:49.700
similar to the one that has hidden truths about UFOs,

01:50.100 --> 01:53.780
non-human intelligences, and physics-redefining technologies,

01:54.200 --> 01:57.600
has also been used to disguise the truth about health.

01:57.720 --> 02:03.040
Following this trail leads through many of the same avenues as the hidden history of UFOs.

02:03.120 --> 02:06.700
The alliance between secret government programs and big business,

02:06.700 --> 02:09.540
classified breakthroughs in science and medicine,

02:09.920 --> 02:12.080
and the code that we have been written on,

02:12.200 --> 02:14.900
our DNA, having cosmic significance.

02:15.300 --> 02:17.760
And there is a conspiracy keeping us poisoned,

02:18.120 --> 02:20.160
low energy, lonely, and tired,

02:20.580 --> 02:23.580
too sick to look up and ask what we are doing here.

02:24.220 --> 02:25.300
But is there a way out?

02:25.600 --> 02:28.960
The long road to the dystopian health system we now live in,

02:29.120 --> 02:30.620
and how it has become enforced,

02:31.120 --> 02:33.760
started at the beginning of the 20th century,

02:33.760 --> 02:36.540
when the entire landscape was transformed,

02:37.100 --> 02:38.320
almost single-handedly,

02:38.620 --> 02:40.760
and to serve big business interests.

02:41.080 --> 02:42.320
John D. Rockefeller,

02:42.540 --> 02:45.720
already the richest man on Earth thanks to Standard Oil,

02:45.980 --> 02:47.040
now ExxonMobil,

02:47.480 --> 02:51.580
had a vision to monopolize medicine in the same way that he had oil.

02:52.260 --> 02:53.760
Petrochemicals were on the rise,

02:53.940 --> 02:57.720
and synthetic pharmaceuticals that included products derived from oil

02:57.720 --> 03:01.140
were a way to patent and own treatments in medicine.

03:01.140 --> 03:04.020
It also meant stamping out competition,

03:04.420 --> 03:09.120
most notably of natural medicine and therapies that could eat into profits.

03:09.420 --> 03:13.960
In 1910, with backing from Rockefeller and fellow titan Andrew Carnegie,

03:14.540 --> 03:16.540
the Flexner Report was released.

03:16.940 --> 03:18.560
Written by Abraham Flexner,

03:18.880 --> 03:21.560
it condemned most of America's medical schools,

03:21.680 --> 03:24.980
especially those teaching anything other than drug-based,

03:25.400 --> 03:26.760
symptom-focused treatment.

03:26.760 --> 03:31.020
Over half the medical schools in the United States shut down.

03:31.300 --> 03:32.820
The rest were brought in line,

03:33.120 --> 03:36.480
and the American Medical Association became the enforcer.

03:36.600 --> 03:39.060
Well, you know who set up the FDA and the AMA,

03:39.340 --> 03:41.080
the American Medical Association and the FDA,

