05:45.820 --> 05:48.180
In the lead-up to the Second World War,

05:48.580 --> 05:52.440
once Imperial Japan had invaded mainland China and Korea,

05:52.840 --> 05:55.940
these occupied territories became the field operations

05:55.940 --> 05:58.220
