24:23.340 --> 24:23.540
You know,

24:23.580 --> 24:25.840
if you put a frog embryo

24:25.840 --> 24:27.420
in a Faraday cage,

24:27.860 --> 24:29.320
it does not develop normally.

24:29.920 --> 24:30.240
And then,

24:30.360 --> 24:32.020
you can change

24:32.020 --> 24:34.720
the cell gradient

24:34.720 --> 24:37.760
of like a tadpole

24:37.760 --> 24:38.740
where you've severed

24:38.740 --> 24:40.180
the arm of the tadpole

24:40.180 --> 24:41.880
to the cell gradients

24:41.880 --> 24:42.760
of the head cells

24:42.760 --> 24:43.520
and you can grow

24:43.520 --> 24:44.140
a, you know,

24:44.200 --> 24:46.100
a chimeric two-headed tadpole.

24:46.440 --> 24:47.720
And so there's something

24:47.720 --> 24:48.500
around kind of

24:48.500 --> 24:49.660
the electromagnetic field

24:49.660 --> 24:51.020
that is orthogonal

24:51.020 --> 24:52.800
and maybe even upstream

24:52.800 --> 24:53.520
of DNA

24:53.520 --> 24:54.780
in terms of morphology.

24:55.780 --> 24:56.000
Yeah,

24:56.040 --> 24:56.440
because I've done

24:56.440 --> 24:57.580
experiments too

24:57.580 --> 24:59.260
with plant growth

24:59.260 --> 25:00.620
around high-powerful

25:00.620 --> 25:01.640
Wi-Fi routers

25:01.640 --> 25:02.420
and that actually

25:02.420 --> 25:03.140
Oh, yeah.

25:03.140 --> 25:04.440
They don't grow right.

25:04.600 --> 25:04.780
No.

25:04.780 --> 25:05.380
It's like pretty,

25:05.700 --> 25:06.640
it's kind of concerning.

25:06.780 --> 25:07.580
I think about the Wi-Fi

25:07.580 --> 25:08.120
in my house.

25:08.200 --> 25:08.440
I'm like,

25:08.480 --> 25:08.760
oh man,

25:08.800 --> 25:09.860
am I like cooking myself

25:09.860 --> 25:10.680
slowly or something?

25:10.680 --> 25:11.460
Have you heard of a guy

25:11.460 --> 25:12.560
named Luc Montagnier

25:12.560 --> 25:13.420
by any chance?

25:13.760 --> 25:14.020
No.

25:14.140 --> 25:14.940
He discovered

25:14.940 --> 25:16.420
the HIV genome

25:16.420 --> 25:18.440
and he's this

25:18.440 --> 25:19.740
French Nobel Prize winner

25:19.740 --> 25:20.900
and at the end

25:20.900 --> 25:21.480
of his life

25:21.480 --> 25:23.560
he was very anti-COVID vaccine

25:23.560 --> 25:24.340
and he said

25:24.340 --> 25:24.880
that there was like

25:24.880 --> 25:26.060
nanotech put in it.

25:26.280 --> 25:26.620
I'm not saying

25:26.620 --> 25:27.240
that's true

25:27.240 --> 25:28.500
but that's what he said.

25:28.980 --> 25:29.800
But he was also

25:29.800 --> 25:30.960
very interested

25:30.960 --> 25:31.700
in this idea

25:31.700 --> 25:32.320
of like

25:32.320 --> 25:35.280
aqueous nanostructures

25:35.280 --> 25:36.160
in the DNA

25:36.160 --> 25:38.200
that transmitted information

25:38.200 --> 25:39.580
via electromagnetism.

25:39.580 --> 25:40.720
And I wonder

25:40.720 --> 25:41.500
if we discover

25:41.500 --> 25:43.500
something in that vein.

25:43.840 --> 25:44.880
Speaking of DNA,

25:45.500 --> 25:47.380
it was just a few years back

25:47.380 --> 25:48.740
when a group of scientists

25:48.740 --> 25:50.260
from Japan and NASA

25:50.260 --> 25:51.740
actually confirmed

25:51.740 --> 25:53.100
something extraordinary.

25:53.500 --> 25:54.920
They reanalyzed fragments

25:54.920 --> 25:56.960
from three ancient meteorites

25:56.960 --> 25:57.700
that had fallen

25:57.700 --> 25:58.420
in Canada,

25:58.740 --> 25:59.260
the US,

25:59.560 --> 26:00.160
and Australia.

26:00.400 --> 26:01.240
And they discovered

26:01.240 --> 26:02.240
that all of them

26:02.240 --> 26:02.880
gave off

26:02.880 --> 26:03.740
the fundamental

26:03.740 --> 26:04.660
building blocks

26:04.660 --> 26:05.760
needed to form

26:05.760 --> 26:07.140
DNA and RNA.

26:07.520 --> 26:08.460
This added weight

26:08.460 --> 26:09.140
to an old

26:09.140 --> 26:10.360
but persistent theory

26:10.360 --> 26:11.100
of the beginning

26:11.100 --> 26:12.260
of life on Earth.

26:12.700 --> 26:13.420
That the spark

26:13.420 --> 26:14.940
had not originated here

26:14.940 --> 26:16.240
but had arrived here.

26:16.480 --> 26:17.360
This is the idea

26:17.360 --> 26:18.440
of panspermia.

26:18.740 --> 26:19.200
The idea

26:19.200 --> 26:20.800
that life's raw ingredients

26:20.800 --> 26:21.940
may have been seeded

26:21.940 --> 26:22.920
across planets

26:22.920 --> 26:23.760
by comets,

26:24.060 --> 26:24.580
asteroids,

26:24.880 --> 26:26.560
or even purposeful design.

26:26.920 --> 26:27.440
In fact,

26:27.560 --> 26:28.020
the idea

26:28.020 --> 26:29.360
of directed panspermia

26:29.360 --> 26:30.140
was proposed

26:30.140 --> 26:31.240
by Francis Crick

26:31.240 --> 26:32.620
who co-discovered

26:32.620 --> 26:33.980
DNA's double helix.

26:34.360 --> 26:35.060
Crick believed

26:35.060 --> 26:35.620
that DNA

26:35.620 --> 26:36.800
was too complex,

26:36.800 --> 26:37.860
too elegant,

26:38.180 --> 26:39.080
and too precise

26:39.080 --> 26:39.940
to have emerged

26:39.940 --> 26:40.760
by accident.

26:40.760 --> 26:41.720
And Crick's view

26:41.720 --> 26:42.100
was,

26:42.340 --> 26:43.700
as a leading

26:43.700 --> 26:45.380
scientist

26:45.380 --> 26:46.640
whose whole life

26:46.640 --> 26:47.180
was focused

26:47.180 --> 26:47.740
on the study

26:47.740 --> 26:48.240
of DNA,

26:48.980 --> 26:49.580
his life was

26:49.580 --> 26:50.080
that DNA

26:50.080 --> 26:50.920
could not have

26:50.920 --> 26:52.140
emerged accidentally

26:52.140 --> 26:54.000
from the primeval soup

26:54.000 --> 26:55.120
on this planet

26:55.120 --> 26:55.960
in just a hundred

26:55.960 --> 26:56.700
million years.

26:57.160 --> 26:57.720
It needed

26:57.720 --> 26:58.600
much longer.

26:59.320 --> 27:00.240
He still bought

27:00.240 --> 27:00.920
into the prime...

27:00.920 --> 27:01.700
What if DNA

27:01.700 --> 27:02.680
was not just

27:02.680 --> 27:03.220
a molecule,

27:03.580 --> 27:04.120
but a kind

27:04.120 --> 27:05.380
of cosmic software,

27:05.840 --> 27:07.280
encoded with instructions

27:07.280 --> 27:08.200
and directed

27:08.200 --> 27:09.240
around the galaxy

27:09.240 --> 27:10.240
with a purpose?

27:10.500 --> 27:11.800
This radical proposal,

27:12.080 --> 27:13.080
from a very important

27:13.080 --> 27:14.140
proponent of modern

27:14.140 --> 27:15.080
Western science,

27:15.260 --> 27:16.480
is also echoed

27:16.480 --> 27:17.500
in ancient cultures.

27:17.660 --> 27:18.860
The recurring motif

27:18.860 --> 27:20.000
of two serpents

27:20.000 --> 27:21.060
twisting together

27:21.060 --> 27:21.820
in a spiral,

27:22.320 --> 27:22.720
like the

27:22.720 --> 27:23.500
Kudaseus,

27:23.840 --> 27:25.060
the staff of Hermes

27:25.060 --> 27:26.020
in Greek mythology,

27:26.440 --> 27:27.980
is still used today

27:27.980 --> 27:28.660
as a symbol

27:28.660 --> 27:29.320
of medicine.

27:29.580 --> 27:30.620
It's almost universal.

27:31.200 --> 27:31.700
You see it

27:31.700 --> 27:32.700
in Hindu temples,

27:33.120 --> 27:34.200
Mesoamerican art,

27:34.700 --> 27:35.700
aboriginal myths,

27:36.140 --> 27:37.300
Sumerian glyphs,

27:37.560 --> 27:38.760
and in the Amazon,

27:39.160 --> 27:40.080
where shamanic

27:40.080 --> 27:41.200
ayahuasca rituals

27:41.200 --> 27:42.180
often produce

27:42.180 --> 27:43.420
visions of serpents

27:43.420 --> 27:44.500
spiraling together,

27:45.140 --> 27:46.520
reportedly the source

27:46.520 --> 27:47.840
of life and knowledge.

27:48.140 --> 27:48.840
Snakes that

27:48.840 --> 27:49.640
ancient traditions

27:49.640 --> 27:51.240
say came from the sky.

27:51.420 --> 27:52.660
So this double helix,

27:52.780 --> 27:53.080
DNA,

27:53.460 --> 27:54.240
might have also

27:54.240 --> 27:55.300
come from the sky.

27:55.580 --> 27:56.100
Could it be

27:56.100 --> 27:57.040
that this symbol,

27:57.380 --> 27:58.240
serpent spiral,

27:58.660 --> 27:59.840
life is more

27:59.840 --> 28:00.840
than just a metaphor?

28:01.420 --> 28:01.780
Could it be

28:01.780 --> 28:02.280
a remnant

28:02.280 --> 28:03.580
of some deeper knowledge,

28:03.900 --> 28:04.940
encoded in myth

28:04.940 --> 28:05.520
and memory?

28:05.720 --> 28:07.340
Even mainstream science

28:07.340 --> 28:08.580
is starting to admit

28:08.580 --> 28:09.340
that DNA

28:09.340 --> 28:10.600
may be stranger

28:10.600 --> 28:11.540
than we thought.

28:11.740 --> 28:12.980
About 98%

28:12.980 --> 28:14.220
of the human genome

28:14.220 --> 28:15.240
does not code

28:15.240 --> 28:15.920
for protein.

28:16.200 --> 28:16.740
For years,

28:16.920 --> 28:17.780
this was dismissed

28:17.780 --> 28:18.840
as junk DNA.

28:19.020 --> 28:19.420
Today,

28:19.580 --> 28:20.360
we know it plays

28:20.360 --> 28:22.340
regulatory and structural roles,

28:22.480 --> 28:23.400
but vast stretches

28:23.400 --> 28:24.220
of this DNA

28:24.220 --> 28:25.720
remain a total mystery.

28:26.140 --> 28:26.880
Some researchers

28:26.880 --> 28:27.580
have proposed

28:27.580 --> 28:28.240
that DNA

28:28.240 --> 28:30.000
with its fractal geometry

28:30.000 --> 28:31.340
and coiled structure

28:31.340 --> 28:32.980
acts like an antenna

28:32.980 --> 28:34.740
capable of responding

28:34.740 --> 28:36.560
to electromagnetic frequencies.

28:37.020 --> 28:38.400
One 2011 study

28:38.400 --> 28:39.740
even described DNA

28:39.740 --> 28:40.700
as possessing

28:40.700 --> 28:41.600
the two key

28:41.600 --> 28:43.040
structural characteristics

28:43.040 --> 28:44.900
of fractal antennas.

28:45.040 --> 28:46.360
In the 1990s,

28:46.460 --> 28:47.380
Russian scientists

28:47.380 --> 28:48.460
described something

28:48.460 --> 28:49.660
even more bizarre.

28:50.060 --> 28:50.900
In their so-called

28:50.900 --> 28:52.560
DNA phantom experiments,

28:52.760 --> 28:53.380
they observed

28:53.380 --> 28:55.120
that after a DNA sample

28:55.120 --> 28:55.860
was removed

28:55.860 --> 28:56.760
from a container,

28:57.140 --> 28:57.820
laser light

28:57.820 --> 28:59.180
continued to scatter

28:59.180 --> 29:00.220
as if the DNA

29:00.220 --> 29:01.340
were still there

29:01.340 --> 29:02.480
for hours,

29:02.780 --> 29:04.080
sometimes days.

29:04.500 --> 29:05.020
The DNA,

29:05.340 --> 29:05.800
it seemed,

29:06.020 --> 29:06.780
left behind

29:06.780 --> 29:08.580
a kind of energetic residue,

29:09.140 --> 29:10.240
a ghostly imprint

29:10.240 --> 29:11.040
in space.

29:11.340 --> 29:11.880
And then,

29:12.000 --> 29:13.700
there are the biophotons,

29:14.060 --> 29:15.480
weak emissions of light

29:15.480 --> 29:16.700
that living cells,

29:16.940 --> 29:17.920
including DNA,

29:18.340 --> 29:19.820
constantly give off.

29:19.820 --> 29:20.720
These emissions

29:20.720 --> 29:21.740
are so faint

29:21.740 --> 29:22.680
that they are difficult

29:22.680 --> 29:23.580
to detect,

29:23.760 --> 29:24.420
but researchers

29:24.420 --> 29:25.400
have speculated

29:25.400 --> 29:26.560
that they might play

29:26.560 --> 29:28.600
a role in cellular communication

29:28.600 --> 29:30.240
or even consciousness.

29:30.800 --> 29:32.520
It is in this liminal space

29:32.520 --> 29:34.440
between rigorous science

29:34.440 --> 29:35.900
and visionary experience

29:35.900 --> 29:37.320
that a new picture

29:37.320 --> 29:38.620
begins to emerge,

29:38.960 --> 29:40.240
one that we now know

29:40.240 --> 29:41.340
so little about

29:41.340 --> 29:42.500
in terms of our current

29:42.500 --> 29:43.460
healthcare system.

29:43.700 --> 29:44.900
A picture where DNA

29:44.900 --> 29:46.020
is much more

29:46.020 --> 29:47.100
than just a molecule,

29:47.480 --> 29:48.340
it may in fact

29:48.340 --> 29:48.960
be a method

29:48.960 --> 29:49.840
of communication,

29:50.380 --> 29:51.340
either over a million

29:51.340 --> 29:52.260
years of time

29:52.260 --> 29:53.600
or perhaps

29:53.600 --> 29:54.360
over a million

29:54.360 --> 29:55.840
light years of space.

29:56.180 --> 29:57.540
And if that is the case

29:57.540 --> 29:58.760
and we are fundamentally

29:58.760 --> 29:59.960
connected to this

29:59.960 --> 30:01.000
cosmic message

30:01.000 --> 30:01.800
that is crucial

30:01.800 --> 30:03.320
for our species to hear,

30:03.620 --> 30:04.600
then we are allowing it

30:04.600 --> 30:06.160
to be slowly cooked off

30:06.160 --> 30:07.100
in the modern world

30:07.100 --> 30:08.680
of ultra-processed foods,

30:09.200 --> 30:10.820
drowning this potential signal

30:10.820 --> 30:11.780
to a higher plane

30:11.780 --> 30:12.500
of consciousness

30:12.500 --> 30:14.340
in sugar and oil.

30:14.520 --> 30:15.280
And while the Department

30:15.280 --> 30:15.840
of Energy,

30:16.340 --> 30:17.140
per the UFO

30:17.140 --> 30:18.180
nuclear connection,

30:18.180 --> 30:19.500
likely holds a lot

30:19.500 --> 30:20.080
of secrets

30:20.080 --> 30:20.740
when it comes

30:20.740 --> 30:21.540
to unidentified

30:21.540 --> 30:22.680
flying objects

30:22.680 --> 30:23.560
and their reverse

30:23.560 --> 30:24.140
engineering,

30:24.540 --> 30:25.760
they also conducted

30:25.760 --> 30:27.160
the Human Genome Project.

30:27.520 --> 30:28.720
So the government agency

30:28.720 --> 30:30.000
that might have proof

30:30.000 --> 30:31.100
that we are not alone

30:31.100 --> 30:31.820
in the universe

30:31.820 --> 30:32.980
also might know

30:32.980 --> 30:34.560
more about the human genome

30:34.560 --> 30:35.700
than any entity

30:35.700 --> 30:36.420
on Earth.

30:36.580 --> 30:37.340
This should all

30:37.340 --> 30:38.160
make you wonder

30:38.160 --> 30:39.940
if whoever is truly

30:39.940 --> 30:41.260
behind this dystopian

30:41.260 --> 30:42.680
reality of modern health

30:42.680 --> 30:43.840
has always had

30:43.840 --> 30:44.380
the intention

30:44.380 --> 30:45.480
of keeping most

30:45.480 --> 30:46.300
of the species

30:46.300 --> 30:47.940
docile and disconnected

30:47.940 --> 30:49.780
from our full human potential.

30:50.100 --> 30:50.700
But I don't want

30:50.700 --> 30:51.560
to be a total bummer

30:51.560 --> 30:52.280
on this topic.

30:52.560 --> 30:53.820
Just like with UFOs,

30:53.900 --> 30:55.120
I believe there is hope

30:55.120 --> 30:55.940
that these systems

30:55.940 --> 30:56.680
can change.

30:56.880 --> 30:57.960
With the Make America

30:57.960 --> 30:59.140
Healthy Again movement,

30:59.340 --> 31:00.340
we've seen massive

31:00.340 --> 31:01.280
leaps of progress

31:01.280 --> 31:02.200
that would have seemed

31:02.200 --> 31:03.660
completely delusional

31:03.660 --> 31:05.580
just a few decades ago.

31:05.640 --> 31:06.600
Because just like

31:06.600 --> 31:07.540
with UFOs,

31:07.900 --> 31:09.300
you do have the agency

31:09.300 --> 31:10.340
to take steps

31:10.340 --> 31:11.800
to disentangle yourself

31:11.800 --> 31:12.720
from the perverse

31:12.720 --> 31:13.860
healthcare environment

31:13.860 --> 31:14.800
that we are living in.

31:14.880 --> 31:15.680
That's exactly

31:15.680 --> 31:16.720
what Ways to Well

31:16.720 --> 31:17.680
is fighting for.

31:17.920 --> 31:19.480
A sense of human agency

31:19.480 --> 31:20.700
and the realization

31:20.700 --> 31:21.740
that so much

31:21.740 --> 31:22.860
of the chronic disease

31:22.860 --> 31:23.660
we live with

31:23.660 --> 31:25.060
is a direct result

31:25.060 --> 31:25.760
of the ways

31:25.760 --> 31:27.220
we've been told to live.

31:27.280 --> 31:28.000
I don't think

31:28.000 --> 31:28.980
we should give up hope

31:28.980 --> 31:29.700
that we can make

31:29.700 --> 31:30.900
our lives healthier,

31:31.340 --> 31:32.400
clean up our environment,

31:32.660 --> 31:34.040
and prevent the diseases

31:34.040 --> 31:35.760
that plunge us into debt,

31:36.180 --> 31:37.740
steal time from our loved ones,

31:38.060 --> 31:38.780
and tether us

31:38.780 --> 31:39.600
to prescriptions

31:39.600 --> 31:40.500
and treatments

31:40.500 --> 31:42.160
that ruin our bodies

31:42.160 --> 31:42.940
and minds.

31:43.860 --> 31:48.640
I swear I already feel better.

31:49.000 --> 31:49.900
It's wild.

31:50.040 --> 31:50.540
I'm here with

31:50.540 --> 31:52.060
now my very good friend,

31:52.160 --> 31:52.660
Brigham Bueller.

31:53.300 --> 31:54.800
I appreciate you having me, man.

31:54.820 --> 31:56.060
We just had the best day

31:56.060 --> 31:57.180
ever at Ways to Well.

31:57.280 --> 31:58.580
I feel amazing.

31:59.000 --> 32:00.100
I did red light therapy,

32:00.540 --> 32:01.280
hyperbaric,

32:01.700 --> 32:02.360
stem cells,

32:02.440 --> 32:03.040
which I've been wanting

32:03.040 --> 32:04.020
to try forever,

32:04.280 --> 32:05.360
and I've heard so many

32:05.360 --> 32:06.120
good things about

32:06.120 --> 32:07.520
and for whatever reason

32:07.520 --> 32:08.500
still has some stigma

32:08.500 --> 32:09.460
when it comes to the FDA,

32:09.600 --> 32:10.180
and I want to talk

32:10.180 --> 32:10.880
about that with you.

32:10.880 --> 32:12.840
But yeah,

32:12.880 --> 32:14.020
we connected around

32:14.020 --> 32:15.480
aliens originally

32:15.480 --> 32:16.620
and UFOs

32:16.620 --> 32:17.220
because that's a deep

32:17.220 --> 32:18.580
interest of yours,

32:18.700 --> 32:19.680
and it's so cool

32:19.680 --> 32:20.600
to see all of this

32:20.600 --> 32:22.820
just UFO-themed,

32:22.960 --> 32:23.660
alien-themed,

32:23.760 --> 32:24.520
but also you're just

32:24.520 --> 32:25.860
helping so many people.

32:26.560 --> 32:27.340
So appreciate you

32:27.340 --> 32:28.000
coming on.

32:28.000 --> 32:29.900
It's funny how we met

32:29.900 --> 32:30.660
because you were going

32:30.660 --> 32:31.420
to give that lecture

32:31.420 --> 32:32.100
in town.

32:32.860 --> 32:33.820
I think the lecture

32:33.820 --> 32:37.100
was about the UAP phenomenon

32:37.100 --> 32:38.780
at a place here in Austin,

32:38.780 --> 32:40.280
and I saw you were in town,

32:40.340 --> 32:41.220
and I just messaged you

32:41.220 --> 32:42.300
to check in and say,

32:42.420 --> 32:42.620
hey,

32:42.800 --> 32:44.160
I would love to connect

32:44.160 --> 32:44.720
while you're here,

32:44.840 --> 32:46.060
and the rest is history.

32:46.200 --> 32:46.680
It's crazy.

32:46.880 --> 32:48.440
I wonder if at some point

32:48.440 --> 32:49.340
in the future

32:49.340 --> 32:50.540
the health stuff

32:50.540 --> 32:52.220
converges with the UFO stuff

32:52.220 --> 32:53.320
and we're able to make

32:53.320 --> 32:55.440
